{"tid":765012,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"突發，摩連奴遭解雇","createTime":"2018-08-02T12:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T15:18:41.000Z","uid":17641,"like":5,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d72d01b810c8636bab1eee168a171539e10a467f","tid":765012,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:07:40.000Z","msg":"周四《BBC》等各大英傳媒率先披露，跌落護級深淵的上季英超盟主車路士，已辭退領隊摩連奴，而消息隨後亦獲車路士官網證實。<br />\n<br />\n帶領車路士7個月前重奪英超冠軍的摩連奴（Jose Mourinho），今季帶隊成績突然一落千丈，開季至今16輪英超竟錄得9場敗仗，目前排名聯賽榜第16位，僅較尾3的諾域治多1分。今季已屢次傳出摩連奴帥位不保，而《BBC》及其他英國各大傳媒在本港時間周四晚上10時半左右，放風指這名領隊已被球會辭退，而車路士官方網站在約半小時後，亦證實一切屬實，刊出官方聲明表示已與摩帥在雙方同意下，解除現有合同。<br />\n<br />\n車仔官方發表的聲明如此說：「球會希望清楚交代，摩連奴是在利好的條件下離開我們，而他將會永遠在球會中，受到愛戴、尊敬，仍是球會最象徵式的人物。他在史丹福橋及英格蘭的傳奇地位，會一直獲所有人認同，球會亦永遠歡迎他再次回來。球會目前希望專注的，是如何令這個有質素的陣容，發揮出它的潛力，直至新帥上任前，我們不會再作任何評論。」<br />\n<br />\n52歲的摩連奴在2013年6月，第2度接掌車路士，首季領軍獲聯賽第3，而去年夏天在購入迪亞高哥斯達及法比加斯等戰將後，為藍軍重奪失落5年的英超錦標。不過，來到今季，球隊縱使早前在歐聯分組賽過關，但聯賽成績意外大幅下滑，而周一作客以1:2負李斯特城後，摩連奴賽後埋怨有感被球員「出賣」，亦有傳與他不和的翼鋒夏薩特，該仗提早傷出，是涉嫌詐傷，不欲為他再賣命。<br />\n<br />\n早前已不斷有報道指出，若摩連奴被解僱，車路士或會再找過去短暫執教球隊的荷蘭名帥軒迪克領軍，而另一熱門人選，還有前熱刺及皇家馬德里主帥拉莫斯。同時，最近盛傳季尾將離開拜仁慕尼黑的哥迪奧拿，有可能成為車仔下季正式主帥。<br />\n<br />\n另外，英國傳媒指車路士會向摩連奴提供1200萬鎊賠償。"},{"pid":"8b59cc227998de6be098d92e3b34ae398adf165e","tid":765012,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ```<br />\n<br />\n車路士"},{"pid":"896e51b8d161ea7ae0b9ffb1451b5d4ada54202a","tid":765012,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:10:18.000Z","msg":"good news<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e34ebd7da275935bb0bce2a184315041a09af3","tid":765012,"uid":105836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:10:34.000Z","msg":"車路士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b351fda57d939ba411ef3586444c5cd26826bbdd","tid":765012,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:12:54.000Z","msg":"歷史不斷重複<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37ffc62f18327eb18fccb998c7c3a2137d005c8","tid":765012,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:38:14.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba770c9275aecc02993b57384658566bdafe76a5","tid":765012,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:55:35.000Z","msg":"雇不到人了"},{"pid":"530e6fd46a544f93580347cbceb183c9db2c5958","tid":765012,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:56:56.000Z","msg":"車仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa812f307c19522b820508663ee6843cf9cbc318","tid":765012,"uid":88461,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T13:02:32.000Z","msg":"頭先有冇人煲衲？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/apmugS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/apmugS</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"011f3e10a82cd86eb8f1976fcdfa457e7dac3d07","tid":765012,"uid":41846,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T13:50:52.000Z","msg":"摩三季"},{"pid":"ae0c1fdd24ea6b152a6bd0a0392aec8a9b7c68cb","tid":765012,"uid":54000,"like"